ActPublic Safety Act, 2002
SubjectOrder Fixing June 1, 2008 certain provisions...
PrecisOrder fixing June 1, 2008 as the day on which certain provisions of the EXPLOSIVES ACT, as enacted by the Public Safety Act, 2002, COME INTO FORCE to allow for the increased control over the importation, exportation, transportation through Canada, aquisition, possession and sale of explosives and certain components of explosives, and provide increased penalties for certain offences.
